data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bed, 2-bath home nestled in the heart of Pleasant Hill. Boasting 1,794 square feet of well-designed living space, the spacious living room connects to the dining area and the well-appointed kitchen. The kitchen is a Chef's dream with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a center island that provides an additional meal prep area as well as an eating bar, soft close drawers, and a generous-sized pantry. The master suite features a separate tub and walk-in shower, double vanities, and a generously sized walk-in closet. The two additional bedrooms are generously sized, allowing for versatility in use – whether as guest rooms, a home office, or a personal retreat. Located a short distance from the community pool and just minutes from Lake Bryan, Rellis Campus, downtown, and all that Bryan/College Station has to offer, this home has it ALL! Don't miss out!!
